WEBVTT

00:00:29.070 --> 00:00:31.722
Brazil is the most violent country
in the world today.

00:00:31.746 --> 00:00:34.775
More people have been dying there
over the last three years

00:00:34.799 --> 00:00:36.196
than in Syria.

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:40.316
And in Mexico, more people have died
over the last 15 years

00:00:40.340 --> 00:00:42.568
than in Iraq or Afghanistan.

00:00:43.256 --> 00:00:47.803
In New Orleans, more people
per capita are dying

00:00:47.827 --> 00:00:49.661
than in war-torn Somalia.

00:00:50.982 --> 00:00:54.193
The fact is, war only results

00:00:54.217 --> 00:00:58.161
in about 18 percent
of violent deaths worldwide.

